title: [Dreamfire Illusions, Backroom]
description: A multicolored assortment of stained glass lanterns provide warm light in this spacious gathering room.  Multiple lotus silk sitting pillows have been arranged in a semicircle with a break to allow for an unobstructed walkway.  On the far side of the room are a variety of tools and storage cabinets, hinting at the room's function as a multipurpose space.
